{"word":"G2700 - κατατοξεύω - katatoxeúō - kat-at-ox-yoo'-o - Thrust through","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατατοξεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katatoxeúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-at-ox-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Thrust through</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எய்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to shoot down or thrust through with an arrow"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5115 - τόξον - tóxon - tox'-on/5115\">G5115</a>; to <i>shoot down</i> with an arrow or other missile: - thrust through.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}